Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:40.48,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}主なき今　風が吹き
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.65,0:01:44.82,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}雲間には　ほら　光が差す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:50.89,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}迷い人は　耳をそばだてて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.99,0:01:56.23,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}自分の道進むための力にする
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:02:02.50,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ココロ折れそうな　長い坂の前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:10.04,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}未来があるなら 背を向けられない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:13.24,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}友よ　覚えているかい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:17.38,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}あの日誓い合ったこの場所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:21.95,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}季節の花が咲く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.52,0:02:25.89,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}主なきその声　聴こえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:29.09,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}太陽が　ほら　少しずつ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:35.60,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}辺りのその闇を剥がしてくれるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:38.80,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}主なき　さぁ　この時に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:42.94,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}僕達は　そう　歩き出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:49.58,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}誰もみんな　弱い生き物さ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:52.45,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}愛の気配　探しながら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:56.05,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}先へ進む
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:40.48,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}没有所属的现在 风儿吹起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.65,0:01:44.82,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}你瞧 光芒穿破云间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:50.89,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}迷茫的人们 竖耳倾听
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.99,0:01:56.23,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}将成为向自己道路前进的动力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:02:02.50,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在让人心折的漫长坡道前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:10.04,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}未来若存在 就必须去面对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:13.24,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}朋友啊 还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:17.38,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}昔日一同起誓的这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:21.95,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}季节的花儿绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.52,0:02:25.89,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}可以听见那没有所属的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:29.09,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}你看 太阳会逐渐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:35.60,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}将周围的黑暗驱除的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:38.80,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}来吧 就在没有所属的这时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:42.94,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}没错 我们要向前迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:49.58,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我们大家都很软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:52.45,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}一边寻找着爱的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:56.05,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}一边向前行进
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:52.72,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Ho！Ho！ Ho！ Ho！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:57.18,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}いつだって夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:59.47,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}遠くに見える
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:03.97,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}届かないくらい距離感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:06.17,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}足元の石を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.40,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ひとつ拾って
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.98,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}がむしゃらになって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:13.14,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}投げてみろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:17.04,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}君の目の前に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:19.31,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}川が流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:23.91,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}広く 大きな川だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:27.19,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}暗く深くても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:31.51,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}流れ速くても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:34.99,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}怯えなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:37.18,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}離れていても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:41.56,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}そうだ 向こう岸はある
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:50.13,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}もっと 自分を信じろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:53.52,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}River !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:55.63,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}AH - AH - AH - AH -
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:58.09,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}自分に言い訳するんじゃねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:00.12,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}AH - AH - AH - AH -
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:02.70,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}やってみなけりゃわかんねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:04.60,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}AH - AH - AH - AH -
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.99,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}まっすぐ進むしかねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:08.89,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ずっと ずっと ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:10.46,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}歩き続けろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:12.48,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}決めた道を !
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:15.66,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}君の心にも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:18.96,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}川が流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:22.38,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}汗と涙の川だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:25.77,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}失敗してしまっても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:30.12,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}流されてしまっても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:33.65,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}やり直せばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:35.85,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}弱音吐くなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:40.00,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}夢にしがみつくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:47.69,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}願い 叶う日が来るまで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.72,0:21:48.60,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}川を渡れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:49.90,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}You can do it !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:57.18,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:59.47,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}梦想总是远在天际
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:03.97,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}让人产生无法靠近的距离感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:06.17,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}将脚下的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.40,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}捡起一块
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.98,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不顾一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:13.14,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}将它投出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:17.04,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在你眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:19.31,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}河水在流淌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:23.91,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}宽广无际的河流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:27.19,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使暗不见底
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:31.51,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使急流恶浪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:34.99,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不必害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:37.18,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使距离遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:41.56,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}也终将抵达彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:50.13,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}再对自己多些自信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:58.09,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不要对自己找借口！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:02.70,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不试试看就不知道结果！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.99,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}只能勇往直前！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:08.89,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}一直 一直 一直
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:10.46,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}向前迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:12.48,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在自己定下的路上！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:15.66,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}你的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:18.96,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}河水也在流淌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:22.38,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}那是汗水与泪水的河流！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:25.77,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使失败
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:30.12,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使被激流卷走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:33.65,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}只要再试一次就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:35.85,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不要说泄气话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:40.00,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}牢牢抓住梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:47.69,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}直到祈愿实现的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.72,0:21:48.60,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}渡过河流！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.66,0:22:29.00,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}いつかの願いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:33.47,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}土の中で眠って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.67,0:22:42.75,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}約束の時刻に 希望の根が出るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:46.75,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}二人が出会った頃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.75,0:22:51.79,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}夢など まだだめだった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:55.69,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}どれくらい時が過ぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:23:01.16,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}花は咲くのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:06.47,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}この涙を君に捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.47,0:23:10.94,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}もっと君が輝くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:16.51,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ずっと見守ってた沈默の空から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.51,0:23:21.15,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}今 僕は雨になろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.52,0:23:24.62,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}あぁ 君に捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.62,0:23:29.26,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}こんな僕に出来ることは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:34.36,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}キミの虚しさを少しでも癒すこと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:39.70,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}さぁ 僕は雨になろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.66,0:22:29.00,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不知何时的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:33.47,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}沉睡在土壤中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.67,0:22:42.75,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在约定好的时间 萌生出希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:46.75,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}当两人相遇之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.75,0:22:51.79,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}梦想还不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:55.69,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不知要过多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:23:01.16,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}花才会绽放呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:06.47,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}把这颗眼泪献给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.47,0:23:10.94,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}如果你能够更加闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:16.51,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我会从一直看着你的沉默的天空中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.51,0:23:21.15,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}成雨落下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.52,0:23:24.62,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}啊 献给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.62,0:23:29.26,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我所能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:34.36,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}就是轻轻抚慰空虚的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:39.70,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}来吧 我将成为雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\3c&HD831D9&\fad(450,450)\pos(1010,64)}-通向剧场之路-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗杀智惠理父亲的凶手还逍遥法外
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是背后有DGTO操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相大概会永远不见天日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理那个样子 会妨碍秋叶星夺还作战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都要让她振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲在自己眼前被杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是多么沉重的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也还没有完全从父亲的死中振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.49,0:00:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们败北 失去演艺的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DGTO的支配就不可动摇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:01:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们0048可是最后的希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 不可以让在黑暗中哭泣的孩子再增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的是啊 我们每个人发出不输给Center Nova的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Takamina姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.99,0:01:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让双晶素产生反应 Kirara极度闪耀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才加姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.48,0:01:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪闪发亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DES军第13输送部队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要进行犯人押送 请求着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认紧急情况 许可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起了 做这样恶趣味的伪装
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真惨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在发源地秋叶星剧场观看公演是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这片天空的颜色到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择了心里上压抑的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让内心不被演艺迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以大家的眼神都那样没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DES那帮家伙做了多么恶劣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有WOTA入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里交战就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不认为粉红色会很可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 Kojiharu姐 很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 小惠 还有76期的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Papa大厨 筹到食材了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些也可以吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的 含有丰富的维他命 还具有药效
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个可以吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了小惠 可以吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再去弄点来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野生偶像 简称野偶的诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长 争气点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tomochin 身体还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tomochin 伤怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 只是头痛得有点厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易来到秋叶星 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找医生 认真治疗一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋叶星的人 憎恨着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认为00抛弃了秋叶星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:05:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退是迫不得已的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了优子 那个时候只有撤退一条路可走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是之后城市立即遭到了占领
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DGTO的宣传充斥了人们的双耳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短短几天居然开始洗脑宣传了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能将天空的颜色传达到网络媒体上去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说这里到底是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是对于我们0048而言 极为神圣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时是连成员也禁止进入的圣域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从来了这里之后就觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能听到什么声音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么声音在身体的深处回响
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tomochin的Kirara…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 动作幅度再大一些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara完全没闪耀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话根本没法让双晶素产生反应的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼 等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做得更好才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再强烈一些 迅速一些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意识到手指的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样 再这样一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样 像这样动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是不甘心全交给成员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己也想登场表演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 现在的翼实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.76,0:07:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在已经做不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 现在只能拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救秋叶星 拯救大家的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼姐哭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位都看到了吧 那就是翼的Kirara的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连毕业已久的翼 都能让Kirara发光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做到这点 就需要超越愿望 超越祈祷的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强烈的思念!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强烈的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些现役成员都做不到 还有何办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连翼这老太婆都豁出去拼命到这个地步了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老 老太婆?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 来拼一把
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别输给老太婆了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连咪酱都这么毒舌啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 继续练习
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的热情点燃了大家的心灵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼酱 GOOD JOB
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不相信她们的话就无从谈起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强烈的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把秋叶星夺回来!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋叶星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最珍贵的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得以实现的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使约定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得以实现的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形形色色的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形形色色的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心怀着各种各样的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想却相同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成为0048
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被梦想所鞭策
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们乘上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往秋叶星的 梦想列车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是 哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.96,0:10:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们 应该是在上排练课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到站了 不过这是哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:10:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Takamina姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开门了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是秋叶星!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个 没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接纳我们梦想的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是秋叶星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara和双晶素产生反应了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定没错 有这种程度的反应的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好真的能做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 做得太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙还没有醒过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙 凪沙!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理是怎么来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道 我 一直在一片黑暗里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在原地不动的话 总觉得会被那片黑暗碾碎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就开始跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定在那时可以忘记一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾见过这番景象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 是不是有人在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧 还真有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不能再往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 第13代啊酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有第6代由依
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他的Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊酱她们在闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可那是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剧场？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊酱就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是却像咫尺天涯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子她怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙 刚才那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 你们看到的毫无疑问是AKB48剧场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AKB48开始于灭亡前的地球上的日本秋叶原的一个小剧场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里集合的少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踏出了梦想的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 地球不是已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大概不是真正的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是由强烈思念所形成的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 优子她并没有到达那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕优子她还并没有完全成为Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那个时候 优子放射出来的的确是Center Nova的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 而且也满足了Center Nova的产生条件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她没有满足Center Nova的消失条件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Center Nova的消失条件？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失的绝对条件是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越时空的可怕的一体感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越时空？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不单和成员 观众 工作人员还有会场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还同未来与过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法用语言表达的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一切融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得无处不在 无处可见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:15:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这带有丝丝恐怖的心醉神迷里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Center Nova消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是优子的那消失方式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却像是独自一人躲进孤独的深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去秋叶星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演唱会会场在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请排队等候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里真的合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合适 翼小姐来过联系了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让Flying get闯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在秋叶星被DES给重重包围
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本闯不进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信00等下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 夺回作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备超空间跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双晶素同步装置正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara驱动器也没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便跳跃成功了 也不知道会到什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舵就交给你来掌了 咪酱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK OK 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kojiharu Tomochin
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也去会场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和演唱会那边会合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先圣老师的传话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tomochin 难道你听得到？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 可并不是语言 而是身体直接感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次夺回秋叶星作战的关键就在于
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NO NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NO NAME 无名的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详细的我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在没时间去想它了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 去准备演唱会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦闯了进去 就开始演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:18:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占领了秋叶星的DGTO绝对会给DES增援
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之前 要把演唱会的气氛炒到最热
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在蓝花星上的演唱会 我发不出声音的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮了我 可我现在却什么忙都帮不上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和爸爸的封闭之门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为我所渴望的都在那道门后面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道如果一直被黑暗吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就永远无法打开那道门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我一定要成为Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抵达那道门的门后面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也为了夺回秋叶星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开那道门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能让智惠理的爸爸领会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居民们已经成功转移
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么万一的话 就由我们来抵挡DES
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快看天空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传送门？难道是00？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去会撞上去 咪酱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天爷保佑我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剧场女神们成功降临了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AKB0048
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有脸回来 你们这些叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚回去 叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前明明那么善良的秋叶星居民
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs30}滚回去 滚回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不抓紧的话 会被DES袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要大家齐心协力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位想想特训的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种场合说要齐心协力…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:20:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋叶星的人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深藏于人们内心深处的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也随着演唱会调动起来 相互联系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.47,0:21:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara和双晶素 假如能对此集体无意识产生反应的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了达到这点 观众们的感情十分重要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.49,0:21:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.79,0:21:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅凭成员们的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能使双晶素产生反应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻里子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Takamina姐 麻里子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论成员们怎么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.01,0:21:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法传达给人们的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.65,0:21:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楚方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋叶星的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.30,0:21:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是那么善良
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的表情却那么可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.35,0:22:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.64,0:22:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DES…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能就此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚回去 滚回去…
